fields.title: Breakout
fields.slogan: LONG, LEAN MUSCLE TAKEN TO THE MODERN EDGE
fields.mainbody: The Breakout is a muscular modern chopper with pure ‘stop you in your tracks’ attitude. Be seen. Be respected. And when the light turns green, be gone.

fields.title: Road King
fields.slogan: STYLE THAT SPEAKS OF DECADES OF LOVE FOR THE OPEN ROAD
fields.mainbody: The stripped-down nostalgic style was born in the ‘60s, but the power of the Milwaukee-Eight® 107 engine brings it all into the right now, fast.

fields.title: Street Glide Special
fields.slogan: KICKS HOT ROD BAGGER STYLE INTO A HIGHER GEAR
fields.mainbody: The custom hot rod bagger look stops people in their tracks. Now powered up with the Milwaukee-Eight® 114 engine, you’ll leave them in your dust.

fields.title: Road Glide Limited
fields.slogan: GOES ALL THE WAY
fields.mainbody: A fully loaded Grand Touring machine with 114 cubic inches of power and new premium finishes. Enjoy the ride to the fullest.

fields.title: Fat Bob
fields.slogan: SHAKE UP THE STATUS QUO
fields.mainbody: The Fat Bob® features aggressive, unapologetic styling, mind-blowing performance and handling, premium finishes, and the massive torque of the Milwaukee-Eight® engine.

fields.title: FXDR 114
fields.slogan: MOVES YOU IN WAYS YOU’VE NEVER BEEN MOVED BEFORE
fields.mainbody: The FXDR™ 114 is a feast for the eyes with performance and attitude that’s off the leash. Fast on the straights. Agile in the corners. It'll blow away your senses.

fields.title: Brutale 1000
fields.slogan: THE FASTEST NAKED BIKE IN THE WORLD
fields.mainbody: The very first Brutale changed the definition of the naked sports bike forever. Today, the Brutale 1000 Serie Oro brings a long pathway of development full circle, whilst marking the beginning of a new concept focused on the pursuit of the ultimate performance.

fields.title: Brutale 800 RR
fields.slogan: THE BEST MIDDLE-WEIGHT NAKED
fields.mainbody: An evolution of the original Brutale, the iconic four-cylinder that rocked the very concept of sports naked

fields.title: Superveloce 800 serie oro
fields.slogan: FULFILL YOUR DESIRE
fields.mainbody: The lines of the Superveloce 800 Serie Oro are a modern interpretation of the iconic stylistic concept of the MV Agusta. A fusion of vintage and contemporary ensures that the future incorporates the memories of good times gone by: 37 world titles, legendary victories, challenges that required going
fields.fronttyre: 120/70 - ZR 17 M/C (58 W) Pirelli Diablo Rosso Corsa II
fields.reartyre: 180/55 - ZR 17 M/C (73 W) Pirelli Diablo Rosso Corsa II

fields.title: F4-RR
fields.slogan: HISTORY IN MOTION
fields.mainbody: A modern classic, the F4 RR set a new paradigm in the world of sports motorcycling. That typical MV feeling; the jaw-dropping performance; the speed; the revolutionary design that redefined the concept of a sports motorbike.
fields.fronttyre: Pirelli Diablo Supercorsa SP 120/70 - ZR 17 M/C (58 W)
fields.reartyre: Pirelli Diablo Supercorsa SP 200/55 - ZR 17 M/C (78 W

fields.title: F3 675
fields.slogan: LEGENDARY INLINE-THREE CYLINDER
fields.mainbody: The F3 675 marks the return, in a production motorcycle, of the legendary three-cylinder engine that dominated the race tracks in the golden age of Giacomo Agostini. This mid-size supersport was also the first to feature a counter-rotating crankshaft.

fields.title: Turismo Veloce 800 RC SCS
fields.slogan: LUXURY. PERFORMANCE. LIMITED EDITION.
fields.mainbody: The luxury edition with electronically controlled semi-active suspension, heated hand grips, central stand and integrated GPS sensor, becomes even more exclusive in this version by Reparto Corse. Only 250 units.

fields.title: Turismo Veloce 800 lusso SCS
fields.slogan: THE SMART TOURER
fields.mainbody: Turismo Veloce 800 Lusso is the model that best represents MV Agusta’s idea of a tourer with no compromises. It introduces the new Smart Clutch system (SCS), an MV proprietary technology that enables the electronic management of the clutch.

fields.title: Dragster 800 RR America
fields.slogan: BLUE, WHITE AND RED
fields.mainbody: The name America has a special place in the history of MV Agusta. The 1975 S America 750 model first comes to mind. It boasted an inline 4-cylinder engine with dual overhead camshaft, 75 hp and air cooling. 25 years on, the 4-cylinder Brutale revived the name America, with its signature colour scheme: blue, white and red.

fields.title: Dragster 800 RR Pirelli
fields.slogan: BEAUTY IS NOT ONLY SKIN DEEP
fields.mainbody: The Dragster 800 RR Pirelli is born from the collaboration between Pirelli and MV Agusta, Italian companies that stand out for their industrial history and are united by values ​​such as Made in Italy design and the vocation to sportiness.
fields.fronttyre: Pirelli Diablo Supercorsa SP 120/70 - ZR 17 M/C (58 W)
fields.reartyre: Pirelli Diablo Supercorsa SP 200/55 - ZR 17 M/C (78 W)

fields.title: Dragster 800 RC
fields.slogan: FROM 0 TO 100 IN A INSTANT
fields.mainbody: Dragster was born to impress, both at rest and while in motion. Reaction at first sight is pure shock, when you hear it screaming you think “I need it!”. We were told this was madness. We didn't listen.

fields.title: Iron 883
fields.slogan: EVERYTHING YOU NEED, NOTHING YOU DON’T
fields.mainbody: An original icon of the Harley-Davidson® Dark Custom style. It sets the standard for the raw, stripped-down, blacked-out look.

fields.title: Ultra Limited
fields.slogan: EXPERIENCE A RIDE THAT IS ANYTHING BUT STANDARD
fields.mainbody: It’s loaded. From the Milwaukee-Eight® 114 engine to the heated hand grips. Classic Batwing fairing, all new BOOM!™ GTS infotainment system, and plenty more. Yes, you can have it all.
fields.frontwheelmaterial: Slicer II cast aluminum with clear coat
fields.rearwheelmaterial: Slicer II cast aluminum with clear coat

fields.title: Fat Boy
fields.slogan: RIPPED, REFINED, AND READY FOR ITS CLOSE-UP
fields.mainbody: The original fat custom icon. Now lighter than the previous generation Fat Boy, and slinging torque from a Milwaukee-Eight® 107 or 114. You’ll feel the difference the instant you crack the throttle.

fields.title: Heritage Classic 114
fields.slogan: FROM THE SHADY SIDE OF THE FAMILY TREE
fields.mainbody: The refined gloss-black finishes, modern edge and reinvigorated ride of the Heritage model take nostalgia ripping into the here and now
